export const body = "RNVI ships with a wide range of icon families. You can also\n[search NPM](https://www.npmjs.com/search?q=keywords%3Areact-native-vector-icons-icon)\nfor third-party icon packages.\n\nBrowse all icons visually in the [Icon Directory](./directory).\n\n## Actively Maintained\n\n| Name | Source | Version | Icons |\n| ---- | ------ | ------- | ----- |\n| [AntDesign](./directory?family=AntDesign) | [Ant Group](https://ant.design/components/icon) | 4.4.2 | 449 |\n| [Feather](./directory?family=Feather) | [Cole Bemis & Contributors](http://feathericons.com) | 4.29.2 | 287 |\n| [FontAwesome](./directory?family=FontAwesome) | [Fonticons, Inc.](https://fontawesome.com/search) | 7.2.0 | 2,806 free / 75,767 pro |\n| [Foundation](./directory?family=Foundation) | [ZURB, Inc.](http://zurb.com/playground/foundation-icon-fonts-3) | 3.0 | 283 |\n| [Ionicons](./directory?family=Ionicons) | [Ionic](https://ionic.io/ionicons) | 8.0.9 | 1,357 |\n| [MaterialDesignIcons](./directory?family=MaterialDesignIcons) | [MaterialDesignIcons.com](https://pictogrammers.com/library/mdi/) | 7.4.47 | 7,448 |\n| [Octicons](./directory?family=Octicons) | [GitHub, Inc.](https://primer.style/foundations/icons) | 19.22.0 | 369 |\n| [Lucide](./directory?family=Lucide) | [Lucide](https://lucide.dev/) | 0.576.0 | 1,950 |\n\n> [!WARNING]\n> FontAwesome Pro icons require a separate licence from\n> [fontawesome.com](https://fontawesome.com).\n> The free icons are included by default; Pro icons require you to provide the font files yourself.\n\n## No Longer Maintained Upstream\n\nThese icon sets are still available but are no longer actively maintained by their original authors.\n\n| Name | Source | Version | Icons |\n| ---- | ------ | ------- | ----- |\n| [Entypo](./directory?family=Entypo) | [Daniel Bruce](http://entypo.com) | 1.0.1 | 411 |\n| [EvilIcons](./directory?family=EvilIcons) | [Alexander Madyankin & Roman Shamin](http://evil-icons.io) | 1.10.1 | 70 |\n| [FontAwesome 4](./directory?family=FontAwesome) | [Fonticons, Inc.](https://fontawesome.com/v4/icons) | 4.7.0 | 786 |\n| [FontAwesome 5](./directory?family=FontAwesome5) | [Fonticons, Inc.](https://fontawesome.com/v5/search) | 5.15.4 | 1,611 free / 7,869 pro |\n| [FontAwesome 6](./directory?family=FontAwesome6) | [Fonticons, Inc.](https://fontawesome.com/search) | 6.7.2 | 2,060 free / 52,663 pro |\n| [Fontisto](./directory?family=Fontisto) | [Kenan Gundogan](https://github.com/kenangundogan/fontisto) | 3.0.4 | 617 |\n| [MaterialIcons](./directory?family=MaterialIcons) | [Google, Inc.](https://fonts.google.com/icons?icon.set=Material+Icons) | 4.0.0 | 2,234 |\n| [SimpleLineIcons](./directory?family=SimpleLineIcons) | [Sabbir & Contributors](https://simplelineicons.github.io/) | 2.5.5 | 189 |\n| [Zocial](./directory?family=Zocial) | [Sam Collins](https://smcllns.github.io/css-social-buttons) | 1.1.1 | 100 |";
